@NODE intro "Introduction"
@{u}Introduction@{uu}

   This is a little door that I believe every multinode MAX's sysop wants! It
allows users on different nodes to communicate with each other (and the sysop
on a local node). It has an IRC style method of working, but it is very simple
to use. As it says, Mega Multinode Chat, it's mega, it's multinode and it's
chat, it does exactly what it says on the tin!

   It also has many useful features, and it is a lot better than the MAX's
internal one! I hope you like it...  oh but don't run Snoopdos! :o)
   
@{u}Requirements@{uu}

MAX's BBS 1.54 68000 version or MAX's Pro.
Fast machine, preferably 030 with fast ram.
`LSD_Doors.key' or `LSD_Otherreg.key' in `Sys:S/'
A multinode BBS.

@ENDNODE


